Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:01.73,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.88,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Hurry! You must remember quickly!}Pospěš si! Musíš si rychle vzpomenout!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.62,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Even with blood armaments, he's still so weak.}Dokonce i s krvavou výzbrojí je stále slabý.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.53,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{He's only just awakened.}Potřebuje se jen probrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.03,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Finish him!}Skonči to s ním!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.04,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry, Chihiro-san.}Promiň, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:25.42,Shinsou - Text - Italic,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't want to lose anyone.}Nechci nikoho ztratit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.77,Shinsou - Text - Italic,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Not ever again!}Už nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.25,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.80,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Ch-Chihiro-san?}Ch-Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:49.21,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you okay, Kotetsu?}Jsi v pohodě, Kotetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:51.90,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:26.00,Ep_Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1400A9&}{Who}Kdo{\c}{ Set} začal {\c&H1400A9&}{Fire}starý{\c}{ to an Old Conflict?} ohnivý konflikt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.50,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{My leg's numb.}Mé nohy znecitlivěli.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.71,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Diabolos have poisonous spears.}Ďáblové mají otrávená kopí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.77,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Poison? What should I do?}Otrávená? Co s tím mám dělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:38.83,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Call my name.}Řekni mé jméno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:39.99,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Your name?}Tvé jméno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.10,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Hurry!}Pospěš!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.39,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Morizono Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.89,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{No, my}Ne, mé {\i1}{real}pravé {\i0}{ name!}jméno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.35,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Remember!}Vzpomeň si!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:55.00,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You should know who I am now!}Měl bys vědět kdo jsem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.74,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:00.86,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes!}Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.54,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are you?}Kdo jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.29,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Let me handle Kotetsu.}Nech to na mě, Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.31,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{So he has a Defender.}Takže on má Ochránce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.23,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Your beloved is a tough one.}Tvůj oblíbenec je těžkej oříšek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.55,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't.}Nedělej to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.05,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san.}Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.98,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you okay, Kotetsu?}Jsi v pohodě, Kotetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:34.62,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.77,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Damn.}Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.51,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Impressive.}Fascinující.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.26,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You killed it with a single blow.}Sejmul jsi ho jednou ranou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.28,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't.}Přestaň.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.08,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:57.59,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{He was a university student \Nhere, just like me.}Stejně jako já, to byl student univerzity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.40,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{And now...}A teď...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.30,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You couldn't have done anything.}Nemohl jsi udělat nic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.36,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{That again?!}Zase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.30,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop using that excuse!}Přestaň se takhle vymlouvat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.82,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{I understand how you feel.}Chápu jak se cítíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:12.22,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{But once someone becomes \Na familiar, there's no going back.}Ale jakmile se někdo stane známým, už není návratu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.31,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You have to kill them.}Musel jsi je zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.92,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Still, I don't want to...}Pořád to ale nechci dělat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.36,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san?}Kakiharo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.81,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I had no idea such monsters existed.}Netušil jsem, že takové příšery existují.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:27.57,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{It's hard to believe, but a journalist\Nbelieves what he sees is the truth.}Je těžké tomu uvěřit, ale i novinář věří tomu co vidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.56,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is a huge scoop.}To bude trhák.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.45,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Now it all makes sense.}Teď to všechno dává smysl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:36.13,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You killed the missing Domyoji\N Rakan the same way, didn't you?}Zabil jsi pohřešovaného Domyoji Rakana stejným způsobem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.09,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I just—}Já jen—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.55,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Well, murder is your forte.}No, vražda je tvá silná stránka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.17,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop!}Přestaňte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.95,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not Chihiro-san's fault!}Není to Chihirova chyba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.88,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Your father was murdered.}Tvůj otec byl zavražděn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.69,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You should know he—}Měl bys vědět, že—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.81,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Again.}Zase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.26,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I can summon it again and again}Můžu ho přivolávat znovu a znovu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.57,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{as long as I have humans to open gates.}tak dlouho dokud lidé otvírají brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.61,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{You did it again!}Udělals to zas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.90,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Death to the Heroic Lineage.}Smrt hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.25,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll do whatever it takes.}Udělám to, co je potřeba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.67,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.08,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.13,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{His blood armaments protected him.}Jeho krvavá výzbroj ho ochránila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.43,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{It's been empowered.}Bylo to oprávněné.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.80,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{No way...}Nemožné...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.19,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll take you on!}Postarám se o něj!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:36.02,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You just had the poison removed. You can't.}Sotva jsi odstranil jed. Nemůžeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.52,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Kill him.}Zabij ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.09,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What's wrong?}Co se děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.89,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Hang in there, Tsubasa!}Vydrž, Tsubaso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.95,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{My head...}Moje hlava...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.58,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Could it be?}Mohlo by to být?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:07.49,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{He's lost control.}Ztratil kontrolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.79,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Hurry up and kill him!}Dělej zabij ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:13.35,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{It's amazing, but...}Je to úžasné, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.02,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{He mustn't.}Nesmí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.36,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{His body won't last if he uses\N his power that way.}Jeho tělo nevydrží, jestli bude používat svou moc tímto způsobem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.40,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.40,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What is this?}Co to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.68,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san...}Kakiharo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.16,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Damn! Why is this happening to Tsubasa?}Sakra. Proč se tohle děje Tsubase?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.38,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Not even an empowered Diabolos can kill him.}Dokonce ani mocný Ďábel ho nemůže zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.63,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Just how much power is hiding in that Vessel?}Kolik energie se skrývá v této nádobě?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.51,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Damn!}Doprdele!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.23,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What should I do?}Co bych měl udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.52,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You should awaken, too.}Měl bys jí také probudit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.98,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are you?}Kdo jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.52,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The Heroic Blood inside you\Nis the only way to save her.}Hrdinská krev je jediný způsob jak jí zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.73,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll do anything!}Cokoliv!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.52,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll do anything, just save her!}Udělám cokoliv, jen když jí to zachrání!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.38,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Save Tsubasa!}Zachraň Tsubasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.73,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Call her name.}Zavolej její jméno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.58,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{The name engraved in the\N memory of your heroic blood.}Jméno je vyryté do paměti vaší hrdinské krve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.70,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Her true name.}Její pravé jméno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.20,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Aero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.13,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tsubasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.13,Shinsou - Text,AERO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's Aero.}Je to Aero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.59,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara, too?}Kakihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.64,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{A Vessel of Heroic Lineage.}Nádoba hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.35,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{A third?}Třetí?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.89,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Heroic Blood calls Heroic Blood.}Hrdinská krev volá hrdinskou krev.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.15,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I misjudged this situation.}Podcenil jsem tuto situaci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.62,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Then I'll at least kill Kamina Chihiro.}Pak alespoň zabiju Kamino Chihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.07,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{This ends here.}Tohle tu končí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.43,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah. We have no choice.}Jo. Nemáme na výběr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.03,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{We'll return and make our report.}Vrátíme se a podáme hlášení.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.45,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Be careful.}Buď opatrný.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.61,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{If you fight like that,\Nyou'll die of blood loss.}Když budeš takhle bojovat, zemřeš na ztrátu krve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:54.93,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are you?}Kdo jsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:57.61,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{My name is Hanashima Shoko.}Jmenuji se Hanashima Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:00.93,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm delighted to meet\Na Vessel of Heroic Lineage.}Jsem potěšena, že potkávám nádobu hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.51,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you all right?}Jsi v pořádku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.31,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the Lord of Creation's...}Ty jsi Pán stvoření ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.36,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Be strong.}Buď silný.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.01,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened to me?}Co se mi to stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.83,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You lost control.}Ztratil jsi kontrolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:15.88,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Lost control?}Ztratil kontrolu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:21.10,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's your fault for behaving recklessly when\Nyou don't even know how to use your power.}Je to tvoje chyba, že se chováš bezohledně, když ani nevíš, jak využít svou moc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.76,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's especially serious in your case,\Nsince your power's so great.}Je to zvláště závažné ve vašem případě, protože vaše moc je tak skvělá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.00,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kamina Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.03,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Turn Tsubasa back to normal!}Vrať Tsubasu do normálu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.70,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is your fault, isn't it?}Není to snad tvoje chyba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.92,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, stop that!}Hej, přestaň s tím!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.92,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What did you do to Tsubasa?!}Co jsi udělal Tsubase?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.72,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.63,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's impossible, Kakihara-san.}To je nemožné, Kakiharo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.92,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.88,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Now that she's a familiar, she\Ncan never be made human again.}Teď, když je známá, nemůže být nikdy zase člověkem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:42.76,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't be ridiculous!}Nebuď směšná!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.44,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Give Tsubasa back!}Proměň Tsubasu zpět!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.69,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{As I've said, it's impossible.}Jak jsem řekla, je to nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:46.55,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san!}Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.51,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Iku-san is...}Iku je...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.62,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.03,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{He couldn't become a familiar.}Nemohl se stát známým.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.85,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're lucky.}Šťastlivec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:00.23,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{This is nearly what happened to Tsubasa-san.}To je skoro to, co se stalo Tsubase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:01.51,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{How is this lucky?!}Jakej šťastlivec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.78,Shinsou - Text,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{That's enough!}Stačí!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.84,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Please! Save Iku-san!}Prosím! Zachraň Ikura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.11,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll take him.}Postarám se o něj.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.59,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are you doing here?}Co tu děláte?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.63,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{He's one of us.}Je jedním z nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.69,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{One of you?}Jedním z nás?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:17.51,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{You must be confused.}Musíte být zmatení.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.92,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Come with me.}Pojďte se mnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:20.91,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Where?}Kam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.17,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Maldeus Church.}Kostel Meldeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:31.27,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Welcome to Maldeus Church.}Vítejte v kostele Meldeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:35.70,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{It is the sacred stronghold of the Heroic\NLineage who fight against Chaos.}Je to posvátná pevnost hrdinské linie, která bojuje proti chaosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.53,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:42.24,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{As their name suggests, they are the forces\N that seek to plunge the world into chaos.}Jak naznačuje jejich jméno, jsou to síly, které chtějí uvrhnout svět do chaosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.81,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Our enemies.}Naši nepřátelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.66,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't get it.}Nepobírám to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.44,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{More importantly, where's Tsubasa?}Mnohem důležitější je, kde je Tsubasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.86,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Aero-san is being examined at the hospital.}Aero je zkoumána v nemocnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.67,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Cerdid-san is with her, so don't worry.}Cerdid je s ní, nemějte starost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.17,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Aero, huh?}Aero, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:03.05,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Hanashima-san, tell us exactly what's going on.}Hanashimo, řekni nám co se tu vlastně děje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.06,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Our leader will tell you.}Náš vůdce ti to řekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.47,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Leader?}Vůdce?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.56,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{"We are such stuff as dreams are made on."}" Jsme stvořeni z toho, co tvoří sny. "
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:16.79,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.88,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{"Yea, all which it inherit, shall dissolve,\N like this insubstantial pageant faded."}Jo, všechno, co to zdědí, se rozloží.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.10,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{When did she get there?}Kdy se tam dostala?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.90,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No way... She's...}Ani náhodou ... Ona je ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.16,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Welcome, Vessels of Heroic Blood.}Vítejte, nádoby hrdinské krve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.96,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I am Dux.}Já jsem Dux.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:36.46,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Dux...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.53,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san, you know her?}Chihiro, ty ji znáš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.08,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I met her once in a dream.}Jednou jsem ji potkal ve snu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:40.98,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{A dream?}Snu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.01,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Dreams are a mirror through\N which we peer into other worlds.}Sny jsou zrcadlem, kterým se díváme do jiných světů.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:48.97,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{We meet again, Kamina Chihiro.}Opět se setkáváme, Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.28,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Impossible.}Nemožné.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.78,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I tagged along for some answers,}Poznamenal jsem si nějaké odpovědi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.86,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{and now some chick wearing\N a weird mask appears.}a najednou se objeví nějaké mládě, co nosí divnou masku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.36,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{How rude.}Jak hrubé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.75,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{All I need to tell the truth is this mouth.}Veškerá pravda, kterou potřebuji říct je v ústech.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.87,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Am I wrong?}Mýlím se?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.60,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Well said.}Dobře řečeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.63,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Judging someone by appearances\Nmakes me a failure of a journalist.}Soudit někoho podle vzhledu je pro mě selhání novináře.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.48,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{No smoking inside the church.}Žádná kouření v kostele.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:17.38,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Tell us. Why is this happening to us?}Řekni nám. Co se nám stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.54,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything is destiny.}Všechno je osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.06,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{That's not an answer.}To není odpověď.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.47,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It begins with the future.}Započalo to s budoucností.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:29.89,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{40 years from now,\N this world will be destroyed.}Od teď za 40 let bude tento svět zničen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.11,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.96,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Eschatology, huh?}Eschatologie, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.14,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is stupid.}To je hloupost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.37,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm simply telling you the truth.}Prostě vám říkám pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:42.53,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Which means those monsters are\Ninvaders, and we have to stop them.}Což znamená, že tyto příšery jsou útočníci a musíme je zastavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.25,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You cannot stop them.}Nemůžete je zastavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:48.11,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Destruction will arrive,\Nand a new world will begin.}Zničení přichází, a nový svět započne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.41,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh? What kind of future is that?}Co? Jaký druh budoucnosti to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.60,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The birth of a new world always\N occurs after destruction.}Zrození nového světa dochází vždy po destrukci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.32,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{And what does that have to do with us?}A co se stane s námi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:02.70,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The new world will be born\Nfrom either hope or chaos,}Nový svět se zrodí z naděje nebo chaosu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.68,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{and the key to that is in the hands\Nof the Vessels of Heroic Blood.}a klíč k tomu je v rukách nádob hrdinské krve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.79,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You.}Vaší.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.98,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Us?}Naší?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:12.43,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are Vessels of Heroic Blood?}Co vlastně znamenají ty nádoby hrdinské krve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:18.22,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{When destruction arrives, a hero named\N the Lord of Vermilion will appear}Když dojde ke zničení, objeví se hrdina jménem Pán Vermilionu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.93,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{and build a new world overflowing with hope.}a vybuduje nový svět plný naděje.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.59,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The Vessels of Heroic Blood\Nare those with the capacity}Nádoby hrdinské krve jsou ti,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.41,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{to become the Lord of Vermilion.}kteří mají schopnost stát se Pánem Vermilionu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.57,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Lord of Vermilion...}Pán Vermilionu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:33.57,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{If the Lord of Vermilion is not born,\Nthe world will be ruled by Chaos.}Pokud se Pán Vermilionu nezrodí, svět bude ovládán Chaosem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.73,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{War, poverty, sickness...}Válka, chudoba, nemoci ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:40.84,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{A chain of terrible events will begin,\N and humanity will sink into despair.}Nastane řetězec děsivých událostí a lidstvo se propadne do zoufalství.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.94,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Not even tabloids would buy that fairy tale.}Dokonce ani bulvár by si nekoupil takovou pohádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.61,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{I thought what you saw with\Nyour eyes was the truth.}Myslela jsem, že jsi viděl pravdu na vlastní oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.92,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Were humans becoming monsters}Lidé se stali příšerami
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.19,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{and your dear assistant transforming\Nall a fairy tale as well?}a vaše drahá asistentka přeměňuje všechny pohádky taky tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.73,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Who are the ones who transformed my dad?}Kdo je ten, který přeměnil mého otce?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.94,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Agents of Chaos.}Agenti Chaosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.24,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Three Vessels of Heroic Blood have awakened,}Tři nádoby hrdinské krve byly probuzeny,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:13.74,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{and all three of them have aligned\N themselves with Maldeus Church?}a všichni tři se přidali k Maldeuskému kostelu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.50,Shinsou - Text,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{I believe so.}Není pochyb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.07,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{They're trying to destroy the world}Snaží se zničit svět
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.17,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{to create their personal paradise.}vytvořit svůj osobní ráj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.50,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Isn't that right, Van Drayle?}Není to tak, Van Drayle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:28.84,Shinsou - Text,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{They claim destruction will arrive in 40 years,}Prohlašují, že ke zničení dojde do 40 let,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.51,Shinsou - Text,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{but it's no big deal.}ale to není tak velký problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.64,Shinsou - Text,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{They're going to destroy it.}Chystají se ho zničit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:38.64,Shinsou - Text,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{But they also claim a world\Nfull of hope will come.}Ale také tvrdí, že přijde svět plný naděje.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.98,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It's sophistry.}Je to sofistika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:44.27,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Even if a utopia will be born,\Nthis world will be destroyed.}Dokonce, i když se utopie zrodí, tento svět bude zničen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.47,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{If the foundation of this new world—\Nthe Heroic Lineage—is eliminated,}Je-li základem pro tento nový svět hrdinská linie, musí být eliminována,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.15,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{then we can escape destruction.}potom se můžeme vyhnout zničení.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.50,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{We must save our world.}Musíme zachránit svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:55.41,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{And to do that, we have our science.}A k tomu máme naši vědu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.67,Shinsou - Text,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Death to the Heroic Lineage!}Smrt hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.92,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{They caused the Great Collapse?}Způsobili Velké zhroucení?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.01,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes.}Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.39,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Because of the Great Collapse,}Protože Velké zhroucení,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.67,Shinsou - Text,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{creatures from other worlds\N are able to enter this one.}stvoření z jiných světů jsou schopni vstupovat do tohoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.39,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{By using living humans as gates.}Používáním živých lidí jako brána.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.68,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Unbelievable.}Neuvěřitelné.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.49,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Tokyo is now a hunting ground\Nfilled with monsters created}Tokio je nyní lovecký areál přeplněný příšerami
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.63,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{to trap and kill the Heroic Lineage.}k chycení a zabití hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.98,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What should we do?}Co bychom měli udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.64,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Survive. That is everything.}Přežít. To je vše.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.69,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Against those monsters?}Proti těmto příšerám?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:28.94,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{There is a way.}Je tu způsob.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.89,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Jaký?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.41,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Destroy Tokyo.}Zničit Tokio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.99,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Once Tokyo is gone, they won't \Nbe able to open any gates.}Jakmile bude Tokio pryč, nebudou moci otevřít žádné brány.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:43.21,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Destroy this city to save your future.}Zničit město pro záchranu budoucnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.34,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.59,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa?}Tsubaso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.44,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Great! You're back to normal.}Skvělé. Jsi v normálu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:54.64,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa?}Tsubaso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.84,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm Aero.}Já jsem Aero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:58.08,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Only her appearance has been restored.}Pouze její vzhled byl obnoven.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:01.71,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Like me, she's not actually Tsubasa-san.}Stejně jako já, není opravdová Tsubasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.06,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you mean?}Co tím myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.63,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{We are Defenders of the Heroic Lineage.}My jsme ochránci hrdinské linie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.32,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{We arrived during the Great Collapse.}Přišli jsme během Velkého zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.96,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{The Great Collapse?}Velkého zhroucení?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.76,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Then when you appeared\Nbefore us, you were already...}Když jste se před námi objevili, už jste ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.23,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.56,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I was simply pretending to be Morizono Eiko.}Jednoduše jsem předstírala, že jsem Morizono Eiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.83,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Then where's the real Morizono-san?}Kde je potom skutečná Morizona?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.29,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't lie to me!}Nelži mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.90,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Even after the Great Collapse,\NTsubasa was the same!}I po Velkém zhroucení byla Tsubasa stejná!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.17,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Some were awakened from the beginning like me.}Někteří byli probuzeni od začátku jako já.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.86,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Others were asleep and unaware, like her.}Jiní spali a nevěděli nic, jako ona.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:37.80,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{She was finally awakened by\N the waves created by Chihiro-san.}Nakonec ji probudili vlny, které vytvořil Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.35,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Waves?}Vlny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.35,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{So it}Takže to {\i1}{is }je{\i0}{your fault!} tvoje chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:45.21,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{How many people do you have\Nto kill before you're satisfied?!}Kolik lidí musí zemřít, než budeš spokojenej?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.35,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If not for you...}Pokud ne pro tebe....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:47.59,Shinsou - Text,KAIKHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Turn her back!}Vrať ji zpět!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.45,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Turn Tsubasa back to her former self!}Vraťte Tsubasu do jejího dřívějšího já.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.00,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Shut up!}Sklapni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.52,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Anyone yelling in the hospital \Nis getting their ass thrown out!}Nakopu prdel každému, kdo bude křičet v nemocnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.98,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry, but it's impossible. I'm—}Omlouvám se, ale je to nemožné. Já—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.01,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened to the real Tsubasa?}Co se stalo skutečné Tsubase?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:02.50,Shinsou - Text,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{All I can say for now is "nowhere."}Jediné co mohu říct je  " nikde ".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.33,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Is she dead?}Je mrtvá?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:09.84,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Not even we know what happens \Nto those we switch places with.}Ani my nevíme, co se stane s těmi, se kterými si prohazujeme místa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:19.84,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're going to leave me too, Tsubasa?}Ty mě taky opustíš, Tsubaso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.24,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You always asked}Vždy ses ptala
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:27.90,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{if it was necessary to \Nstubbornly pursue Kamina.}zda bylo nutná tvrdohlavě sledovat Kamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.73,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{And I ignored you.}Ale já tě ignoroval.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.83,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this my fault?}Je to má chyba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.75,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Did this happen to you because\N I wouldn't stop following him?}Stalo se ti to, protože jsem ho nepřestal sledovat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:43.55,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{No. It's all}Ne. Všechno je to {\i1}{his}jeho{\i0} {fault!}chyba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.94,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kamina Chihiro's fault!}Chyba Kamina Chihiry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.43,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I will avenge you.}Já tě pomstím.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.56,Shinsou - Text,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Until everything becomes clear,\N I'll hold on, even if it kills me.}Dokud nebude vše jasné, vydržím to, dokonce i kdyby mě to mělo zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.45,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:58.30,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{He shouldn't change any further, for now.}Pro teď by se neměl proměňovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.75,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Iku-san.}Iku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:02.72,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I've been secretly taking\N in people like Ikuro-san}Tajně jsem bral lidi jako je Ikuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:06.18,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{who have become partially merged\Nwith creatures of other worlds.}kteří se částečně sloučili se stvořením jiných světů.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.94,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Can he be cured?}Může být vyléčen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.23,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not that easy.}Není to tak lehké.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.22,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Cerdid, you guys must know something.}Cerdid, musíte něco vědět.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.82,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't be ridiculous.}Nebuď směšný.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:19.03,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{We were simply summoned from beyond.}Byli jsme jednoduše předvoláni z druhé strany.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.33,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{By the Great Collapse?}Velkým zhroucením?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.20,Shinsou - Text,EIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes.}Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:28.15,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Humans have an unidentified\N gene known as the Arcana gene.}Lidé mají neidentifikovaný gen známý jako gen Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.71,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Arcana gene?}Gen Arcana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:34.74,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{"What is the soul?" It's the\Neternal scientific question.}„Co je duše?“ Je to věčná vědecká otázka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.25,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Apparently this gene is related\Nto some spiritual quality.}Zřejmě tento gen souvisí s nějakou duchovní kvalitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.47,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{The same Arcana gene exists in you all,}Ten samý gen existuje ve vás všech,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.37,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{as well as the creatures from \Nother dimensions and worlds,}stejně jako stvoření z jiných dimenzí a světů,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:46.60,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{and they resonate with one another.}a navzájem rezonují.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.25,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{When that resonance strengthens,}Když tato rezonance posiluje,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.91,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{creatures from other worlds\N cross into our dimension.}stvoření z jiných světů skrz naší dimenzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.47,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{They use humans with strong connections\N to their Arcana genes, turn them into gates,}Používají lidi se silným spojením se svými Arcana geny, přičemž je přeměňují do bran,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.97,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{and enter this world.}a vstupují na tento svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.58,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{And that was suddenly brought about...}A to bylo najednou způsobeno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.00,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{...by the Great Collapse.}Velkým zhroucením.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.92,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Though some can coexist with their\Nhuman forms like Cerdid and Aero,}Ačkoli někteří mohou koexistovat s jejich lidskými formami jako Cerdid a Aero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:12.00,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{those who can't withstand being used\Nas gates seem to vanish into a red mist.}ti, kteří nemohou odolat tomu, aby se používali jako brány, zřejmě zmizí do rudé mlhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.79,Shinsou - Text,KOTETU,0000,0000,0000,,{Iku-san won't turn into the red mist, will he?}Iku se nezmění v rudou mlhu, že ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.19,Shinsou - Text,INUKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll keep treating him.}Budu se o něj starat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.51,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Can he be cured?}Může být vyléčen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.50,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{You just don't get it.}Prostě to nechápete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.51,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{We're working on it right now!}Pracujeme na tom právě teď!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.47,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.47,Shinsou - Text - Italic,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this my fault?}Je to má chyba?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:29.74,Shinsou - Text - Italic,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Because of your involvement with me, even you...}Kvůli svému zapojení se mnou, dokonce i ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.56,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{And if that's true?}A co když je to pravda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:40.60,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The stench of death that clings \Nto you pulls in those around you.}Pach smrti, který tě obklopuje, vtahuje lidi okolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.17,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.32,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Such a tragedy.}Taková tragédie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:52.21,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything disappears, and all \Nthat ever remains is you.}Všichni a všechno zmizí, dokud nezbydeš jen ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:53.60,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Dux!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.80,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It's all your fault.}Vše je to tvá chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.76,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No. I didn't do anything.}Ne. Nic jsem neudělal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.70,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Then what is that in your hand?}Potom, co to držíš v ruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.70,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{It was the same back then.}Tehdy to bylo stejné.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.87,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Please stop. I...}Prosím přestaň. Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:19.82,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes. That hand has been\N stained with blood since then.}Ano. Ta ruka byla od té doby poskvrněna krví.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:21.89,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Forgive me.}Odpusťte mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.78,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Do you seek salvation?}Hledáš spásu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:30.30,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Even inevitable tragedies\N sometimes receive applause.}Dokonce i nevyhnutelné tragédie občas dostávají potlesk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.98,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, so long as the tragedy\N you invite has meaning.}Ano, tak dlouho dokud zveš tragédie, to má smysl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.79,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:39.24,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Even if your hands are stained with\Nblood and everything is destroyed,}Dokonce, i když jsou tvé ruce zbarveny krví a vše je zničeno,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.97,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{as long as hope lies beyond it,}pokud naděje leží na druhé straně,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.51,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{the blood you spill will\Nbe the foundation of the future.}krev, kterou proliješ bude základem budoucnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.81,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't escape your fate.}Nemůžeš utéct svému osudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.89,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{However, if you insist \Non seeking forgiveness...}Nicméně, pokud budeš trvat na hledání odpuštění...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.17,Shinsou - Text,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{You must choose.}Musíš si vybrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.40,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Dux! Dux!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.59,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Is something wrong?}Je něco špatně?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:03.80,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Where's Dux?}Kde je Dux?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.83,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.87,Shinsou - Text,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-san, your hand...}Chihiro, tvá ruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.87,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, come on! Don't hurt yourself in a hospital!}Ale no tak! Neubližuj si v nemocnici!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:16.20,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh? There's no wound.}Co? Nemáš žádné zranění.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.38,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{This is old, isn't it?}Není to staré?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.18,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't!}Přestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.32,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{What's your problem?}Co máš za problém?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.97,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{S-Sorry.}Omlouvám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.27,Shinsou - Text,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't get you.}Nechápu tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.85,Shinsou - Text,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{So long as it has meaning, huh?}Tak dlouho, jak to má smysl, co?
